## More findings - 3 (last)

From the finding 2, we have to execute the endpoints two times to see the both enabled and hidden weakness types. To merge and show the complete order result, we can put in the ```team_weakness``` node in the ```Team``` object of the ```Insights``` function, this list all the sorted weakness types regardless of their states (enabled / disabled / hidden). The following code is added to the endpoint query:

```
team_weaknesses{edges{node{report_count,state,weakness{name,external_id}}}}
```

